definitions.definition: The middle bone of the proximal series of the carpus in the wrist , which is shaped like a half-moon .
An observation of a lunar distance ( “ the angle between the Moon and another celestial body ” ) , especially for establishing the longitude of a ship at sea .

main_definition: ( anatomy ) The middle bone of the proximal series of the carpus in the wrist , which is shaped like a half-moon .
